WEBVTT

00:22.920 --> 00:24.850
I want to negotiate a deal with you.

00:25.960 --> 00:26.890
Can these things

00:27.320 --> 00:27.960
be made?

00:28.440 --> 00:30.370
I need them the day after tomorrow.

00:31.070 --> 00:32.670
Do you think I'm omnipotent?

00:33.070 --> 00:35.600
Signal arrows, fire thunderstone,
and sleeve daggers.

00:35.600 --> 00:36.430
You think these things

00:36.430 --> 00:37.880
can be conjured up just like that?

00:37.880 --> 00:40.520
You and Yuan Xiaoliu can make it in time.

00:44.070 --> 00:45.600
I'll pay extra. Double.

00:49.670 --> 00:50.560
Triple.

00:50.880 --> 00:52.210
I can't afford any more.

00:52.320 --> 00:55.070
Discussing money between friends
makes things awkward.

00:55.070 --> 00:56.670
You know what I want the most.

01:00.880 --> 01:02.600
Alright, I promise you.

01:03.240 --> 01:05.560
Li Lejun won't be chosen
for a political marriage.

01:05.560 --> 01:06.120
Deal.

01:11.310 --> 01:12.950
Are these the places you and Yizhi

01:12.950 --> 01:14.350
want to travel to in the future?

01:14.350 --> 01:16.610
Yes, these are all places I want to visit.

01:16.710 --> 01:17.789
Master Yuan told me

01:18.000 --> 01:19.400
there are special ores

01:19.400 --> 01:20.730
in some of these places.

01:20.920 --> 01:22.400
It sounds very interesting.

01:22.400 --> 01:23.530
I want to take a look.

01:27.590 --> 01:29.000
Here, here,

01:29.280 --> 01:30.010
and here.

01:30.500 --> 01:32.960
There are bandits
at the border. Be careful.

01:33.590 --> 01:35.039
If it's convenient for you,

01:35.039 --> 01:37.200
you can tell me the route
you are going to take.

01:37.200 --> 01:38.350
There is a geomancer in the army,

01:38.350 --> 01:39.810
who can draw a detailed map

01:39.840 --> 01:41.170
to avoid any omissions.

01:41.479 --> 01:42.310
Xiao Wuyi,

01:42.680 --> 01:43.640
having you as a friend

01:43.640 --> 01:44.700
is a true treasure.

01:46.070 --> 01:46.710
Then when the time comes,

01:46.710 --> 01:48.200
can I also use your name

01:48.200 --> 01:49.860
to stay in the Beifu Army Camp?

01:52.070 --> 01:52.930
In your dreams.

01:53.310 --> 01:54.920
You are not a military family member.

01:54.920 --> 01:57.520
Don't even think about
taking advantage of me.

03:25.920 --> 03:29.840
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

03:30.079 --> 03:32.730
[Episode 11]

03:33.840 --> 03:34.430
Wuyi.

03:37.710 --> 03:38.750
Congratulations.

03:38.750 --> 03:40.410
You had a great victory today.

03:41.750 --> 03:42.560
How is Da?

03:42.800 --> 03:43.750
He was injured by an arrow,

03:43.750 --> 03:45.030
but his life is not in danger.

03:45.030 --> 03:46.030
He made contributions in this battle.

03:46.030 --> 03:48.079
His Majesty has agreed
to transfer him to the Imperial Guard.

03:48.079 --> 03:49.740
He will be back by my side soon.

03:50.560 --> 03:51.290
That's good.

03:55.120 --> 03:56.650
When did you start planning

03:57.560 --> 03:58.760
the matter of Heximu?

04:00.150 --> 04:01.880
Before returning to Jiankang.

04:04.830 --> 04:06.020
That's our Wuyi,

04:06.430 --> 04:07.840
never missing a single detail.

04:07.840 --> 04:08.900
Now, the Eagle King

04:08.960 --> 04:10.000
has also been forced by you

04:10.000 --> 04:11.730
to sit down and have a good talk.

04:16.800 --> 04:17.430
Wuyi.

04:19.360 --> 04:20.959
If I want to contend with you,

04:21.560 --> 04:23.220
do I have the qualifications?

04:39.310 --> 04:41.510
The Eagle King bet the three prefectures,

04:41.510 --> 04:42.970
and I bet the name of Beifu.

04:43.310 --> 04:44.770
What are you fighting for?

04:45.270 --> 04:46.159
What is the bet?

04:47.040 --> 04:47.770
I don't know.

04:49.270 --> 04:50.560
Perhaps after a fight,

04:51.270 --> 04:52.330
I will understand.

05:11.870 --> 05:14.600
I saw everything
in the martial arts arena today.

05:14.750 --> 05:15.870
You like Xie Jiayu?

05:23.070 --> 05:23.720
Yes.

05:24.560 --> 05:25.620
You are shameless.

05:25.630 --> 05:27.690
Before I knew she was the one you love,

05:28.510 --> 05:30.720
I had fallen in love
with Xie Jiayu at first sight.

05:30.720 --> 05:32.180
But you are my best friend.

05:32.390 --> 05:33.270
And now you know.

05:33.270 --> 05:34.730
So I have done nothing now.

05:36.000 --> 05:38.130
She is still waiting to leave with you.

05:41.040 --> 05:43.000
You're the one who doesn't want to leave.

05:43.000 --> 05:43.950
So what if I am?

05:46.360 --> 05:47.560
I'm betting Xie Jiayu

05:48.310 --> 05:49.480
on this arrow.

05:52.560 --> 05:53.760
Xie Jiayu is a person.

05:54.040 --> 05:55.070
She has feelings

05:55.070 --> 05:56.200
and a life of her own.

05:56.310 --> 05:57.600
She shouldn't sacrifice for anyone

05:57.600 --> 05:59.130
or be controlled by anyone.

06:00.070 --> 06:00.750
Yizhi,

06:01.920 --> 06:03.450
you told me this yourself.

06:11.430 --> 06:12.760
Whether to stay or leave

06:13.560 --> 06:14.630
is up to you.

06:25.310 --> 06:27.170
Whether Xie Jiayu stays or leaves

06:27.720 --> 06:28.870
is up to her as well.

07:03.430 --> 07:04.430
Ziqi.

07:16.750 --> 07:19.880
I remember you've liked
sour food since you were little.

07:20.430 --> 07:22.630
These sour plum cakes are made

07:22.630 --> 07:23.680
from fresh seasonal plums.

07:23.680 --> 07:24.390
Try some.

07:28.600 --> 07:29.270
How is it?

07:30.310 --> 07:31.430
When I was in the army,

07:31.430 --> 07:32.750
I missed your cooking.

07:35.000 --> 07:35.870
Next,

07:36.680 --> 07:37.830
what are your plans?

07:38.159 --> 07:40.040
Now that the three prefectures
are settled,

07:40.040 --> 07:41.510
my peace talks
with Northern Qin are still ongoing—

07:41.510 --> 07:43.120
Who asked about the peace talks?

07:43.120 --> 07:46.120
I'm asking about your marriage.

07:47.700 --> 07:48.960
My proposal for reform

07:49.120 --> 07:50.159
touches the interests of noble families.

07:50.159 --> 07:51.270
The Empress Dowager
hasn't declared her stance,

07:51.270 --> 07:52.630
but she'll definitely have misgivings
about the marriage

07:52.630 --> 07:53.630
between the He and Xiao families.

07:53.630 --> 07:54.890
When the time is right,

07:55.120 --> 07:56.630
I will end this marriage

07:57.040 --> 07:58.480
and give He Yuanji her freedom,

07:58.480 --> 08:00.210
-so that she and Yao can—
-Wuyi.

08:00.680 --> 08:01.750
What I mean is,

08:02.160 --> 08:03.420
life is a long journey.

08:03.480 --> 08:04.610
Walking hand in hand

08:05.040 --> 08:06.680
beats going alone.

08:08.480 --> 08:10.720
I really don't want you

08:11.120 --> 08:12.120
to be truly alone.

08:14.160 --> 08:17.290
When you fell off your horse
and fell into a coma that day,

08:17.320 --> 08:18.510
Jiayu came to me

08:19.190 --> 08:20.850
and told me to be fairer to you.

08:22.360 --> 08:24.600
Although she doesn't know the whole story,

08:24.600 --> 08:26.660
she can still see your difficulties.

08:27.240 --> 08:29.510
I can see she's a good girl,

08:30.120 --> 08:32.110
and she cares for you.

08:34.320 --> 08:36.320
Xie Jiayu is pure and kind-hearted,

08:37.080 --> 08:39.480
but she already has someone she likes.

08:39.840 --> 08:40.750
So what?

08:41.240 --> 08:43.039
Even if she's a kite
in someone else's hands,

08:43.039 --> 08:44.010
if you like her,

08:44.960 --> 08:46.960
what's the harm in fighting for her?

08:47.270 --> 08:50.320
Besides, you now hold the string.

08:50.550 --> 08:52.840
In terms of status, you lose to no one.

08:53.120 --> 08:55.510
Are you telling me to snatch her?

08:55.530 --> 08:56.770
You're a grown man.

08:57.870 --> 08:59.550
What's the harm in fighting for her?

08:59.550 --> 09:01.350
But I promised Princess Yunzhao

09:01.440 --> 09:03.320
to give Xie Jiayu the freedom to choose.

09:03.320 --> 09:06.080
You've met Princess Yunzhao?

09:06.390 --> 09:07.750
For the path I must take,

09:08.580 --> 09:10.980
I've already dragged the Xiao family down.

09:11.200 --> 09:13.330
I don't want to implicate anyone else.

09:13.910 --> 09:14.480
Darling!

09:15.320 --> 09:16.630
I caught a big fish!

09:17.270 --> 09:18.440
Your son is useless.

09:18.550 --> 09:20.350
He didn't even catch half a fish.

09:21.750 --> 09:23.080
Your father is really

09:23.270 --> 09:24.330
naughty by nature.

09:36.280 --> 09:36.830
Come on.

09:41.910 --> 09:43.170
Let me refill your cup.

09:43.790 --> 09:44.240
Okay.

09:44.720 --> 09:45.780
I'll fill mine too.

09:46.510 --> 09:49.910
Yuezhou, one of the three prefectures
awarded in this competition,

09:49.910 --> 09:53.270
is where my husband died in battle.

09:53.600 --> 09:55.460
Ruisheng, I've heard you say this

09:56.000 --> 09:58.200
3 times already.

10:00.240 --> 10:01.480
I'm just happy.

10:02.960 --> 10:04.220
If his spirit in heaven

10:04.960 --> 10:07.020
knew that Yuezhou had returned to Ye,

10:08.360 --> 10:09.630
he would be thrilled.

10:09.870 --> 10:12.270
Then Ruisheng, was your husband

10:12.390 --> 10:14.270
handsome?

10:14.440 --> 10:15.440
Of course.

10:16.360 --> 10:18.400
Otherwise, why would I have chosen him?

10:18.400 --> 10:21.200
He couldn't even afford
the betrothal gifts then.

10:22.000 --> 10:24.550
Is your man handsome?

10:24.870 --> 10:26.960
Right, is he handsome?

10:35.240 --> 10:36.040
I understand.

10:37.790 --> 10:39.450
If you think about it that way,

10:39.870 --> 10:41.400
Xiao Wuyi is quite pitiful.

10:41.480 --> 10:42.880
He is so good at fighting.

10:42.960 --> 10:44.480
But he’s been married 3 times.

10:44.480 --> 10:45.750
And no one wants him.

10:46.550 --> 10:47.960
-Coming.
-Let me tell you.

10:47.960 --> 10:50.270
-He has a bad temper.
-Let's go, Ziqi. Let's play in the water.

10:50.270 --> 10:52.670
-In fact, he is a good man.
-Let's go, Ruisheng.

10:52.670 --> 10:54.670
It's just that his temper is too bad.

10:57.030 --> 10:57.790
Xie Jiayu,

10:58.720 --> 11:00.380
what did you just say about me?

11:01.270 --> 11:03.200
Ruisheng, I... I'll also go...

11:03.390 --> 11:03.870
go...

11:04.070 --> 11:05.070
play in the water.

11:06.840 --> 11:08.110
Good. Very good.

11:08.750 --> 11:10.680
I've never seen such a good person.

11:13.960 --> 11:14.650
What is this?

11:14.650 --> 11:16.750
This is Li Lejun's
new Four Pillars of Destiny Chart.

11:16.750 --> 11:17.850
Whether from the perspective
of Northern Qin

11:17.850 --> 11:20.080
or Southern Ye's calendar and astrology,

11:20.080 --> 11:22.080
hers and the Eagle King's
are a sign of great misfortune.

11:22.080 --> 11:23.880
Put this in the royal genealogy.

11:24.030 --> 11:25.230
I hope it can help her.

11:25.360 --> 11:26.910
Okay, thanks.

11:27.960 --> 11:29.550
I've only been married once.

11:29.550 --> 11:31.480
I don't need your pity.

11:33.840 --> 11:34.550
I

11:35.030 --> 11:36.480
do have a bad temper.

11:38.000 --> 11:38.790
No.

11:45.750 --> 11:46.360
These are

11:46.360 --> 11:48.690
my ideas for upgrading the Beifu weapons.

11:48.910 --> 11:50.270
Some are already perfected,

11:50.270 --> 11:51.670
and some still need work.

11:52.120 --> 11:52.840
On the day of the Double Ninth Ceremony,

11:52.840 --> 11:54.000
I promised the Beifu soldiers

11:54.000 --> 11:55.460
to upgrade their weapons.

11:55.790 --> 11:57.450
I will never break my promise.

11:58.600 --> 11:59.120
Well...

11:59.650 --> 12:01.600
most of the designs are whimsical.

12:02.170 --> 12:03.500
But the talent is there.

12:04.480 --> 12:06.030
Why don't you come with me to Beifu?

12:06.030 --> 12:07.390
Designing weapons

12:07.510 --> 12:09.270
is different from constructing mechanisms.

12:09.270 --> 12:11.240
It requires examining the local terrain,

12:11.240 --> 12:12.670
weather, and tactics.

12:12.670 --> 12:13.360
Stop.

12:14.670 --> 12:16.030
I want to leave Xiao Wuyi,

12:16.030 --> 12:17.150
not be sold to him.

12:17.550 --> 12:20.390
Besides, you just want to trick me into
the Directorate of Military Equipment,

12:20.390 --> 12:22.450
so you can slack off yourself, right?

12:22.630 --> 12:23.550
You.

12:23.960 --> 12:25.390
You are just like your mother.

12:25.390 --> 12:27.510
You keep saying you
want to roam the martial arts world

12:27.510 --> 12:29.150
and wander to the ends of the earth.

12:29.150 --> 12:31.750
Then let me ask you,
where is the martial arts world?

12:31.750 --> 12:33.480
And where are the ends of the earth?

12:33.480 --> 12:34.220
-Martial arts world...
-Look,

12:34.220 --> 12:35.150
you can't answer, can you?

12:35.150 --> 12:36.950
You just want to travel and play.

12:37.080 --> 12:38.030
Let me tell you.

12:38.440 --> 12:39.720
At this time of year,

12:40.320 --> 12:42.840
Heading south,
there are rainstorms and floods.

12:42.840 --> 12:44.630
Heading north, there are sandstorms.

12:44.630 --> 12:46.550
Heading west,
there are high mountains and steep hills.

12:46.550 --> 12:47.610
Most importantly,

12:47.910 --> 12:50.310
bandit rebellions occur from time to time.

12:51.030 --> 12:52.240
Still, I shouldn't be scared

12:52.240 --> 12:53.440
before I even go, right?

12:53.440 --> 12:54.170
That's true.

12:57.120 --> 12:58.360
Why don't you take me as your master?

12:58.360 --> 12:59.550
I'll take you to see

12:59.550 --> 13:01.080
the desert roses

13:01.270 --> 13:02.720
and yellow phosphorus mines you like.

13:02.720 --> 13:03.780
Most importantly,

13:03.840 --> 13:04.550
as your master, I

13:04.550 --> 13:06.120
will pass on everything I've learned

13:06.120 --> 13:07.270
in my life to you,

13:07.910 --> 13:09.030
making your mechanism designs

13:09.030 --> 13:11.690
benefit the people's livelihood
in the future.

13:12.030 --> 13:12.550
Then...

13:13.320 --> 13:14.850
can I bring a family member?

13:16.150 --> 13:18.150
I won't ask who this person is first.

13:18.790 --> 13:19.840
Is he willing?

13:20.390 --> 13:21.360
As a dignified man,

13:21.360 --> 13:23.030
doesn't he have his own ambitions?

13:23.030 --> 13:23.550
He...

13:45.440 --> 13:46.320
Picking a wife?

13:49.120 --> 13:49.750
Thanks.

13:52.440 --> 13:54.600
That Xie girl is so quick to catch on.

13:55.150 --> 13:56.880
After some persuasion from me,

13:56.910 --> 13:58.720
she's already tempted

13:58.720 --> 14:00.720
by the idea of becoming my disciple.

14:01.350 --> 14:01.960
Also,

14:02.150 --> 14:04.360
what amazing luck you have.

14:04.790 --> 14:05.850
To have the heavens

14:05.960 --> 14:07.750
send you such a treasure.

14:12.840 --> 14:14.040
Do you look familiar?

14:14.910 --> 14:15.790
Caltrop fireball.

14:15.790 --> 14:18.630
Xie tinkered with this herself

14:18.630 --> 14:19.910
after reading ancient books.

14:19.910 --> 14:21.480
It perfectly matches

14:21.480 --> 14:22.940
my previous design ideas.

14:23.200 --> 14:24.270
Such talent

14:24.630 --> 14:26.200
indeed shouldn't be buried

14:26.200 --> 14:28.260
in the romance of the inner quarters.

14:29.200 --> 14:31.000
You've really found a treasure.

14:35.670 --> 14:38.190
[Divorce Agreement]

14:41.390 --> 14:42.630
You like Xie Jiayu?

14:43.910 --> 14:44.440
Yes.

14:45.240 --> 14:47.100
Whether Xie Jiayu stays or leaves

14:47.240 --> 14:48.360
is up to her as well.

14:56.150 --> 14:58.530
[Palace of Eternal Peace]

14:59.750 --> 15:02.200
Her Majesty has selected
some princesses for you, Your Highness.

15:02.200 --> 15:04.960
This is the legitimate daughter
of Lord Liu, Vice Censor-in-Chief.

15:04.960 --> 15:05.790
She is 15.

15:06.080 --> 15:07.270
She is well-versed in poetry and books,

15:07.270 --> 15:08.910
and is best at playing the guqin.

15:08.910 --> 15:11.960
This one is the niece
of Lord Zhao, Director of the Secretariat.

15:11.960 --> 15:12.960
She has practiced martial arts
since childhood.

15:12.960 --> 15:13.960
She has a valiant temperament,

15:13.960 --> 15:15.560
truly a heroine among women.

15:18.360 --> 15:18.870
Lejun.

15:20.120 --> 15:20.550
Come.

15:22.840 --> 15:24.390
Do you think Yaoyao prefers moon white

15:24.390 --> 15:25.320
or azure?

15:25.550 --> 15:27.630
Let's wait for her to choose for herself.

15:27.630 --> 15:28.200
Brother.

15:28.480 --> 15:30.680
She usually likes to study those tools.

15:31.000 --> 15:32.030
But the palace has many rules,

15:32.030 --> 15:33.030
and it's not safe.

15:33.080 --> 15:35.880
I'm afraid it will be hard
for her to enjoy herself.

15:36.440 --> 15:38.640
She also likes to listen to storybooks.

15:38.960 --> 15:40.030
We can keep some entertainers

15:40.030 --> 15:41.030
to make her happy.

15:41.750 --> 15:42.910
As for the Imperial Cuisine Department,

15:42.910 --> 15:44.270
I also sent someone to adjust

15:44.270 --> 15:46.130
the menus according to her taste.

15:46.570 --> 15:47.550
Hurry and help me think

15:47.550 --> 15:48.790
if there's anything else I've missed.

15:48.790 --> 15:49.390
Brother,

15:49.840 --> 15:50.770
does Yaoyao know

15:51.080 --> 15:52.840
that you don't plan to leave Jiankang

15:52.840 --> 15:55.240
but still want to bring her
into the palace?

15:55.480 --> 15:56.870
As long as I can be with her,

15:56.870 --> 15:58.930
what difference does it make
whether we leave Jiankang or not?

15:58.930 --> 16:00.790
How could there be no difference?

16:01.440 --> 16:02.970
Yaoyao yearns for freedom,

16:03.360 --> 16:05.150
but you want her to live
in the deep palace for a long time.

16:05.150 --> 16:06.410
Don't you understand?

16:06.550 --> 16:08.390
Yaoyao can give up the name of Xie Jiayu

16:08.390 --> 16:09.840
to travel the world with you.

16:09.840 --> 16:11.550
But she won't give up
the name of Xie Jiayu

16:11.550 --> 16:12.720
to enter the palace with you.

16:12.720 --> 16:14.960
Besides, there are these women.

16:15.960 --> 16:17.760
These are all stopgap measures.

16:18.600 --> 16:20.400
Yaoyao will surely understand.

16:21.230 --> 16:23.550
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

16:27.870 --> 16:28.960
Over the past few days, one after another,

16:28.960 --> 16:31.120
prominent families have sent
portraits to the Eastern Palace.

16:31.120 --> 16:32.670
It seems they intend to propose marriage.

16:32.670 --> 16:34.960
It looks like Prince Qi
is determined not to leave.

16:34.960 --> 16:36.510
Lady Xie is still in the dark.

16:36.510 --> 16:37.670
These past few days,
she's been busy preparing

16:37.670 --> 16:39.320
parting gifts for everyone in the mansion.

16:39.320 --> 16:40.320
For the Heir's Consort,

16:40.320 --> 16:41.390
it's a paperweight.

16:41.390 --> 16:42.200
For Madam Ruisheng,

16:42.200 --> 16:43.750
it's a brand-new set of
acupuncture needles.

16:43.750 --> 16:44.840
For the Prince and the Princess,

16:44.840 --> 16:46.720
it's a suit of armor and a bladed hairpin.

16:46.720 --> 16:47.510
A single slash severs the throat.

16:47.510 --> 16:48.840
The fastest way to slaughter a chicken.

16:48.840 --> 16:49.790
For Ziqi, it's a stack of

16:49.790 --> 16:51.910
classic books she hasn't even finished
reading herself.

16:51.910 --> 16:52.510
That's it?

16:53.240 --> 16:55.440
Yan Yue and I
got a pair of new shoes each.

16:56.960 --> 16:57.630
Calm down.

17:01.600 --> 17:02.460
Your Highness.

17:02.910 --> 17:04.069
The Eagle King suddenly
went back on his word.

17:04.069 --> 17:06.270
He wants to add terms to the peace talks.

17:07.750 --> 17:09.640
If you interrupt
my medical practice again,

17:09.640 --> 17:11.569
you will have to find someone else.

17:12.480 --> 17:13.880
He still hasn't given up.

17:14.510 --> 17:15.910
What are his conditions?

17:16.550 --> 17:17.150
What is it?

17:29.200 --> 17:29.790
Leave us.

17:30.590 --> 17:31.160
Yes.

17:35.200 --> 17:35.750
Brother,

17:36.590 --> 17:37.450
what happened?

17:37.550 --> 17:40.440
Lejun, did you meet the Eagle King once?

17:41.200 --> 17:41.790
Yes.

17:46.480 --> 17:48.170
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

17:48.170 --> 17:50.480
I thought he would make
things difficult in public,

17:50.480 --> 17:52.350
but he didn't mention it later.

17:53.000 --> 17:54.790
I thought the poisoning matter

17:54.790 --> 17:56.440
couldn't be brought out into the open.

17:56.440 --> 17:57.750
Her Majesty and the Eagle King

17:57.750 --> 17:59.340
probably wouldn't do anything to me.

17:59.340 --> 18:00.590
So I was relieved.

18:01.160 --> 18:02.880
Why? Is the Eagle King

18:02.880 --> 18:04.480
blackmailing you with this?

18:07.510 --> 18:09.440
The Eagle King intends
to treat you as a princess

18:09.440 --> 18:10.960
for a political marriage
with Northern Qin,

18:10.960 --> 18:12.720
to show the sincerity of the peace talks
between the two countries.

18:12.720 --> 18:13.590
What?

18:14.400 --> 18:15.600
Political marriage?

18:18.270 --> 18:18.880
Brother.

18:21.270 --> 18:23.240
Don't worry, I will protect you.

18:23.830 --> 18:26.290
I will never let you
marry into Northern Qin.

18:29.010 --> 18:30.100
[Ziji Palace]

18:33.680 --> 18:35.440
This is the legitimate daughter
of Minister Cao, Commandant of Justice.

18:35.440 --> 18:36.680
She knows 6 languages

18:37.160 --> 18:39.480
and can assist you
with foreign affairs, Your Highness.

18:39.480 --> 18:42.350
This is the younger sister
of the Left Palace Guard General.

18:42.350 --> 18:43.510
She is excellent at brewing tea.

18:43.510 --> 18:47.350
Upon tasting it, I find it surpasses
the Nanzhao Xueya tea by quite a margin.

18:47.350 --> 18:48.160
It seems

18:48.920 --> 18:51.320
it's hard for you
to find a good match today.

18:53.640 --> 18:56.440
He Tian, take everyone away.

18:57.310 --> 18:57.790
Yes.

18:59.110 --> 19:00.170
Take them all away.

19:00.200 --> 19:00.860
-Yes.
-Yes.

19:08.110 --> 19:10.110
Sorry to trouble you, Your Majesty.

19:10.550 --> 19:11.350
It's nothing.

19:12.550 --> 19:15.400
Although I couldn't find
a good match for you today,

19:15.400 --> 19:18.260
there is another
excellent marriage arrangement.

19:24.310 --> 19:25.720
The day before yesterday,

19:25.720 --> 19:27.640
the Eagle King
sent an envoy to the palace,

19:27.640 --> 19:30.720
who said the Eagle King
admires Princess Pingning's virtues,

19:30.720 --> 19:33.400
is willing to offer the 1,000-li grassland
in Monan as a betrothal gift,

19:33.400 --> 19:34.750
and use the etiquette for a royal princess

19:34.750 --> 19:37.150
to ask for the hand of your sister,
Li Lejun.

19:37.480 --> 19:40.160
I think this
is an excellent marriage arrangement,

19:40.160 --> 19:43.360
so I accepted the marriage document
and betrothal gifts.

19:43.480 --> 19:44.540
Please take a look.

19:56.790 --> 19:59.750
Recently, Northern Qin and our Ye

19:59.750 --> 20:01.550
are about to sign a peace treaty.

20:02.240 --> 20:03.200
Our people at Northern Border

20:03.200 --> 20:04.930
will no longer suffer from war.

20:05.030 --> 20:06.830
If we can have a political marriage
with Northern Qin,

20:06.830 --> 20:08.690
wouldn't it be a blessing for our people

20:08.690 --> 20:09.820
and for Ye?

20:22.750 --> 20:25.110
Your Majesty, peace talks
do not mean begging for peace.

20:25.110 --> 20:26.160
If we just keep yielding,

20:26.160 --> 20:27.640
it will only make
Northern Qin more arrogant.

20:27.640 --> 20:29.160
Today, he dares to ask for my sister.

20:29.160 --> 20:31.560
Tomorrow, he will dare
to ask for Jiankang.

20:32.680 --> 20:34.160
Please reconsider, Your Majesty.

20:34.160 --> 20:35.030
Reconsider?

20:36.590 --> 20:37.830
If I reconsider,

20:38.140 --> 20:40.670
Princess Pingning
will have left the palace!

20:51.680 --> 20:52.750
Bring her in!

20:53.240 --> 20:54.030
Bring her in.

20:56.940 --> 20:59.460
Today, I want to see

21:00.270 --> 21:02.880
who dares to take Li Lejun away

21:03.270 --> 21:04.670
and ruin the peace talks.

21:10.720 --> 21:11.160
Lejun!

21:12.070 --> 21:12.590
Lejun!

21:13.760 --> 21:14.350
Brother.

21:22.480 --> 21:25.010
Princess Pingning
left the palace secretly,

21:25.240 --> 21:26.570
ruining the peace talks

21:26.640 --> 21:28.570
and disregarding the safety of Ye.

21:29.200 --> 21:29.730
Beat her!

21:32.070 --> 21:32.550
Lejun!

21:32.590 --> 21:33.390
Your Majesty!

21:34.030 --> 21:34.830
Your Majesty!

21:36.960 --> 21:37.760
Your Majesty!

21:37.960 --> 21:39.440
I was the one who didn't want
Lejun to enter a political marriage.

21:39.440 --> 21:40.760
I was the one who sent someone
to take her out of the palace.

21:40.760 --> 21:41.960
The one who should be beaten

21:41.960 --> 21:43.270
should be me, Your Majesty!

21:43.270 --> 21:43.750
No,

21:44.200 --> 21:45.130
that's not true.

21:45.310 --> 21:48.240
Your Majesty, this has nothing
to do with my brother.

21:48.270 --> 21:49.790
I didn't want to marry the Eagle King,

21:49.790 --> 21:50.920
so I ran away secretly.

21:50.920 --> 21:53.480
If you want to punish someone,
punish me alone.

21:53.480 --> 21:54.940
Don't involve my brother.

21:55.200 --> 21:55.750
Lejun.

21:55.750 --> 21:56.350
Brother.

21:57.310 --> 21:58.240
I know

21:58.830 --> 22:00.200
that you love me

22:00.640 --> 22:02.160
and want to take the blame for me.

22:02.160 --> 22:04.360
But you really knew nothing about this.

22:05.070 --> 22:08.280
Your Majesty, I did all this alone.

22:08.920 --> 22:10.030
Please punish me.

22:10.270 --> 22:11.030
Good.

22:12.110 --> 22:14.510
What a deep bond
between brother and sister.

22:14.510 --> 22:16.040
Then I will grant your wish.

22:16.270 --> 22:18.070
Prince Qi failed in his duty
of supervision

22:18.070 --> 22:19.640
and will receive 30 strokes of the cane.

22:19.640 --> 22:23.500
Princess Pingning will take the punishment
on behalf of her brother.

22:26.750 --> 22:27.950
Mercy, Your Majesty!

22:29.750 --> 22:30.950
Mercy, Your Majesty!

22:32.240 --> 22:34.040
You can't do this, Your Majesty!

22:34.110 --> 22:34.910
Your Majesty!

22:35.400 --> 22:36.200
Your Majesty!

22:36.640 --> 22:38.440
You can't do this, Your Majesty!

22:38.880 --> 22:40.210
-Lejun.
-Pass my order.

22:40.350 --> 22:42.030
Princess Pingning, Li Lejun,

22:42.350 --> 22:43.830
with the rites of a princess,

22:43.830 --> 22:46.230
shall marry the Eagle King
of Northern Qin.

22:46.400 --> 22:48.200
She is the pillar
of our diplomatic relations

22:48.200 --> 22:50.000
and the core of the peace treaty.

22:50.030 --> 22:53.560
Let the people of Jiankang
decorate with flowers and lanterns,

22:53.720 --> 22:55.000
sweep the streets,

22:55.440 --> 22:57.790
and celebrate the grand ceremony
of her royal carriage's departure,

22:57.790 --> 23:01.590
to manifest the virtue of eternal peace
between the North and South.

23:01.890 --> 23:02.610
-Yes.
-Yes.

23:27.240 --> 23:29.770
Your Highness, are you here
for the political marriage?

23:29.770 --> 23:32.170
Your Highness, I beg you
to spare my sister.

23:33.270 --> 23:34.130
Your Highness.

23:34.830 --> 23:36.830
Look at who these people are first.

23:37.400 --> 23:39.240
These two are spies sent by you.

23:39.920 --> 23:41.920
For a bite of food and a sip of water,

23:42.440 --> 23:44.240
they live like beasts of burden.

23:44.240 --> 23:46.510
If your Southern Ye and our Northern Qin
form a political marriage,

23:46.510 --> 23:47.400
these people

23:47.790 --> 23:49.720
might live more like human beings.

23:50.160 --> 23:51.220
So, Your Highness,

23:51.270 --> 23:54.200
between Princess Pingning
and the beasts of burden,

23:54.400 --> 23:55.600
who would you choose?

23:57.400 --> 23:59.720
And who would Xiao Wuyi choose?

24:00.360 --> 24:02.090
But why does it have to be Lejun?

24:02.550 --> 24:03.550
The political marriage

24:03.550 --> 24:05.830
was not in the terms of the peace talks
in the first place.

24:05.830 --> 24:07.160
I lost the competition,

24:07.480 --> 24:08.680
and I am very unhappy.

24:09.790 --> 24:11.480
That day, the Empress Dowager
of your Southern Ye

24:11.480 --> 24:12.830
prepared poison arrows,

24:12.830 --> 24:14.490
which was truly disgraceful.

24:14.680 --> 24:16.810
But your sister is quite interesting.

24:17.000 --> 24:18.130
She broke the arrow.

24:18.350 --> 24:19.480
Even though she was in deep trouble,

24:19.480 --> 24:21.030
she still wanted to save others.

24:21.030 --> 24:22.440
Shouldn't such a stubborn flower

24:22.440 --> 24:24.680
bloom in the north wind,

24:24.960 --> 24:25.590
should it?

24:33.380 --> 24:33.820
You...

24:35.720 --> 24:36.780
What are you doing?

24:37.270 --> 24:38.800
You're in the capital of Ye.

24:43.070 --> 24:45.270
Who can prove they are from Southern Ye?

24:45.920 --> 24:48.250
Negotiations require bargaining chips.

24:48.880 --> 24:49.810
In Northern Qin,

24:49.920 --> 24:51.720
we respect heroes like Xiao Wuyi

24:51.830 --> 24:54.590
who have waded through mountains
of swords and seas of blood.

24:54.590 --> 24:56.400
If he twists the truth out of thin air,

24:56.400 --> 24:59.330
who would dare to disagree
in your Southern Ye court?

25:03.880 --> 25:04.920
So, Prince Qi,

25:06.310 --> 25:07.310
what do you have?

25:08.640 --> 25:10.770
You are just an empty shell of a Regent,

25:12.840 --> 25:14.370
unfit to negotiate with me.

25:16.640 --> 25:18.500
I will not let my sister marry you.

25:35.400 --> 25:36.730
The day I became Regent,

25:37.750 --> 25:39.280
who was the one who chose me?

25:39.350 --> 25:40.550
Was it His Majesty

25:42.200 --> 25:43.070
or you, Master?

25:44.600 --> 25:45.600
It was me.

25:48.550 --> 25:51.790
Your Highness, can you tell me today

25:53.070 --> 25:55.070
if I made the wrong choice?

25:59.830 --> 26:01.310
What I learned in the past

26:02.310 --> 26:03.640
was all about the way of a gentleman

26:03.640 --> 26:05.300
and the principles of living.

26:05.680 --> 26:06.640
From now on,

26:07.550 --> 26:09.880
please teach me the way of a ruler

26:10.550 --> 26:11.950
and the art of an emperor.

26:13.110 --> 26:15.110
Have you really thought it through,

26:15.640 --> 26:16.970
not to leave with Jiayu?

26:21.520 --> 26:22.980
As long as I can save Lejun.

26:25.920 --> 26:29.640
This path is destined to only go forward,

26:31.160 --> 26:32.360
with no turning back.

26:35.200 --> 26:37.000
What is sincerity worth anyway?

26:37.000 --> 26:39.000
How dare you come here
and bargain with me?

26:39.000 --> 26:40.590
Everything you have now

26:41.030 --> 26:43.430
was bestowed upon you
by His Majesty and me.

26:44.460 --> 26:45.860
If I decide not to give it,

26:46.310 --> 26:47.910
then you shall have nothing.

26:51.510 --> 26:52.710
I want to have power.

26:53.640 --> 26:55.790
I don't want to be empty-handed anymore,

26:55.790 --> 26:57.050
threatened by others,

26:57.440 --> 26:58.500
and at their mercy.

27:07.580 --> 27:09.640
You and I both know well what Xiao Wuyi

27:09.960 --> 27:12.220
aims to achieve with his reform of Beifu.

27:12.640 --> 27:14.310
The peace talks are temporary.

27:14.310 --> 27:16.000
You're just taking advantage of the fact

27:16.000 --> 27:17.510
that Northern Qin
is currently in political chaos

27:17.510 --> 27:19.440
to gain some breathing room, aren't you?

27:19.440 --> 27:22.110
If Xiao Wuyi really succeeds in the reform

27:22.110 --> 27:23.880
and centralizes military power,

27:23.880 --> 27:25.960
it will weaken the power
of your noble families

27:25.960 --> 27:28.020
and pose a threat to our Northern Qin.

27:28.480 --> 27:29.720
So, reasonably speaking,

27:29.720 --> 27:31.070
we should cooperate.

27:33.750 --> 27:35.920
You want me to commit treason?

27:36.910 --> 27:39.740
Your Highness, having tea is fine,

27:40.640 --> 27:43.400
but your appetite is too big.

27:44.720 --> 27:46.880
And you can't give me what I want.

27:47.550 --> 27:48.640
What do you want?

27:48.920 --> 27:50.160
The truth about

27:51.270 --> 27:53.240
the treason case
involving the An and Lu families

27:53.240 --> 27:54.880
of Ye 25 years ago.

27:59.920 --> 28:01.380
I can't help you with that.

28:01.440 --> 28:03.030
I was just a child back then.

28:03.510 --> 28:05.920
Let the Empress Dowager
of Northern Qin come talk to me.

28:05.920 --> 28:07.120
She's in the Capital.

28:09.070 --> 28:09.750
Is she?

28:11.510 --> 28:12.840
Where else would she be?

28:15.030 --> 28:17.920
I can give you another greeting gift

28:18.110 --> 28:20.170
to show my sincerity in cooperation.

28:27.160 --> 28:27.760
Xiao Wuyi.

28:29.350 --> 28:31.440
Whether the peace talks succeed or not,

28:31.440 --> 28:32.700
Li Lejun cannot marry.

28:32.880 --> 28:34.230
The peace talks must succeed.

28:34.230 --> 28:35.290
I'm not asking you.

28:35.550 --> 28:37.810
I'm just telling you what I'm going to do.

28:37.880 --> 28:39.830
I know what the peace talks mean to you.

28:39.830 --> 28:41.630
But Lejun is more important to me

28:42.270 --> 28:43.510
than anyone else.

28:55.590 --> 28:57.170
Your Highness, you should tell Prince Qi

28:57.170 --> 28:59.370
that you're already figuring out a way.

29:01.000 --> 29:02.600
The rift has already formed.

29:03.920 --> 29:05.450
There's no need to say more.

29:06.640 --> 29:09.210
[Xiyue Restaurant]

29:09.010 --> 29:11.030
How is the investigation
of the Northern Qin delegation going?

29:11.030 --> 29:12.310
As you ordered, Your Highness,

29:12.310 --> 29:14.110
I sent people to keep a close eye
on Honglu Temple.

29:14.110 --> 29:15.720
I also bought
the night soil collector off.

29:15.720 --> 29:17.350
Judging from the medicine dregs,

29:17.350 --> 29:20.080
someone in the delegation
must be seriously ill,

29:20.270 --> 29:22.110
and it's an elderly woman.

29:22.480 --> 29:23.960
Her status is quite high.

29:31.870 --> 29:33.330
Northwestern tiger bone.

29:33.720 --> 29:34.780
Liaoshan ginseng.

29:39.440 --> 29:40.570
South Sea agarwood.

29:40.830 --> 29:41.760
Quite precious.

29:42.510 --> 29:44.670
This woman must have
an extraordinary identity.

29:44.670 --> 29:45.700
High status,

29:45.720 --> 29:47.580
yet not on the delegation's list.

29:47.920 --> 29:49.790
Either the person's identity
is inconvenient to reveal,

29:49.790 --> 29:51.310
or their purpose is.

29:52.510 --> 29:54.070
Is this the great merit you mentioned?

29:54.070 --> 29:54.870
There's more.

29:55.350 --> 29:56.920
I had people watch for several days

29:56.920 --> 29:58.160
before finally catching up with these two

29:58.160 --> 30:00.270
Northern Qin people
who went to the clinic to buy medicine.

30:00.270 --> 30:01.480
Here comes the interesting part.

30:01.480 --> 30:02.400
Guess what?

30:02.880 --> 30:04.200
These two Northern Qin people

30:04.200 --> 30:06.160
-look familiar—
-Spare me your storytelling.

30:06.160 --> 30:07.090
Get to the point.

30:07.200 --> 30:08.800
These two were once at Xiyue Restaurant,

30:08.800 --> 30:09.900
listening for several days

30:09.900 --> 30:11.640
to the storybooks of Crown Prince Wenxi.

30:11.640 --> 30:13.200
They also sent people to inquire

30:13.200 --> 30:16.200
about Crown Prince Wenxi
and the Phoenix Heart Token.

30:17.640 --> 30:18.400
Great.

30:19.310 --> 30:20.600
If the mountain won't come to me,

30:20.600 --> 30:22.000
I will go to the mountain.

30:22.260 --> 30:24.990
I'll use the Phoenix Heart Token
to draw them out.

30:27.030 --> 30:30.160
Have Honglu Temple reorganize
the peace talk proposals.

30:30.160 --> 30:31.440
Apart from the three prefectures,

30:31.440 --> 30:33.700
see if there is any room for negotiation.

30:33.700 --> 30:36.030
The Eagle King just wants
to prove a point.

30:36.720 --> 30:38.720
The Eagle King has always wanted
the smelting technique for refined iron,

30:38.720 --> 30:41.120
even offering 800 fine horses in exchange.

30:41.640 --> 30:43.040
This is non-negotiable.

31:00.120 --> 31:00.800
Spit it out.

31:03.880 --> 31:04.680
Spit what out?

31:04.720 --> 31:05.720
Words to scold me.

31:06.240 --> 31:07.770
Haven't you heard the news?

31:09.640 --> 31:11.920
I did have a lot to say to scold you.

31:14.110 --> 31:16.240
But you look so weighed down
with troubles.

31:16.240 --> 31:16.900
Never mind.

31:23.310 --> 31:24.240
What did Mao say?

31:25.450 --> 31:29.050
He won't let Li Lejun enter
a political marriage, no matter what,

31:30.000 --> 31:31.350
at any cost.

31:32.140 --> 31:34.070
Mao and Lejun only have each other.

31:34.830 --> 31:36.560
It's only right for him to do so.

31:38.110 --> 31:39.510
But to you, Xiao Wuyi,

31:40.510 --> 31:42.570
ensuring the peace talks go smoothly

31:42.720 --> 31:44.720
and buying time for the Beifu reform

31:45.350 --> 31:47.080
are the most important things.

31:51.640 --> 31:52.240
Yes.

31:53.030 --> 31:53.790
Though,

31:55.350 --> 31:57.010
you know what Lejun will face.

32:05.510 --> 32:06.110
All right.

32:09.640 --> 32:10.240
That's it?

32:11.910 --> 32:14.220
I thought you would argue with me,

32:15.640 --> 32:17.790
calling me a liar, cold-blooded,

32:18.720 --> 32:19.980
and worse than a beast.

32:21.230 --> 32:22.030
Xiao Wuyi,

32:22.310 --> 32:23.400
in your heart,

32:23.590 --> 32:25.110
am I that unreasonable?

32:25.110 --> 32:27.240
Have you ever been reasonable with me?

32:35.230 --> 32:37.960
You have already changed
Lejun's birth records.

32:38.550 --> 32:39.880
You've done all you can.

32:40.550 --> 32:42.750
The instigator today is the Eagle King.

32:43.110 --> 32:44.570
You only made your choice.

32:46.680 --> 32:47.810
You are not to blame.

32:54.160 --> 32:55.470
What's with that look?

32:57.440 --> 32:58.070
Nothing.

32:58.440 --> 32:59.400
I don't know either.

32:59.400 --> 33:00.480
Probably because

33:01.270 --> 33:03.930
it's the first time
I've heard someone say that,

33:04.310 --> 33:05.310
so it feels fresh.

33:06.510 --> 33:07.110
However,

33:08.270 --> 33:09.830
I will still stop this.

33:11.920 --> 33:13.780
If Lejun were a pampered princess

33:14.680 --> 33:16.080
supported by the people,

33:16.880 --> 33:19.160
then she would shoulder
the responsibility of the world now,

33:19.160 --> 33:20.690
and I'd have nothing to say.

33:20.990 --> 33:21.840
But she is not.

33:26.310 --> 33:27.240
Qizhou fell.

33:28.640 --> 33:30.240
Mao and Lejun fled all the way

33:31.070 --> 33:32.000
to Jiankang.

33:32.790 --> 33:33.550
Did His Majesty and Her Majesty

33:33.550 --> 33:35.480
ever care for them for a single day?

33:36.480 --> 33:38.720
They only have the status
of the royal family in name,

33:38.720 --> 33:40.780
but live worse than ordinary people.

33:41.240 --> 33:42.500
To support the family,

33:42.590 --> 33:44.790
Lejun has been copying books for others

33:44.790 --> 33:46.720
and doing needlework since childhood.

33:46.720 --> 33:48.070
She was already weak.

33:48.920 --> 33:51.200
If my mother hadn't known
some medical skills

33:51.200 --> 33:53.200
and hadn't found out
Lejun had an old illness,

33:53.200 --> 33:55.000
she would have barely survived.

33:55.720 --> 33:58.380
This is not the ending
a good person should have.

34:01.030 --> 34:02.640
How do you plan to stop it?

34:03.270 --> 34:04.000
Don't worry.

34:05.310 --> 34:06.270
My method

34:07.200 --> 34:09.130
has nothing to do with your empire.

34:13.320 --> 34:14.320
Being your friend

34:16.030 --> 34:16.889
is quite lucky.

34:20.710 --> 34:21.370
You forgot.

34:24.590 --> 34:25.850
You are also my friend.

35:01.700 --> 35:05.120
♪ A dying memory glimmers low ♪

35:05.420 --> 35:09.090
♪ You appear, but I can't hold you so ♪

35:06.280 --> 35:07.410
I'm here to save you!

35:09.200 --> 35:13.570
♪ Time itself comes to a sudden halt ♪

35:13.930 --> 35:16.620
♪ So desolate ♪

35:17.200 --> 35:20.870
♪ I traded obsession for this loss ♪

35:19.760 --> 35:20.840
Someone like you

35:20.900 --> 35:24.440
♪ If I could lay my heart bare and cross ♪

35:21.440 --> 35:23.240
is born to be on the battlefield,

35:23.540 --> 35:24.760
to make everyone fear you.

35:24.620 --> 35:29.960
♪ Would you once more have pity on me ♪

35:30.600 --> 35:34.040
♪ If the heavens should change
and fate tear me apart ♪

35:34.060 --> 35:38.060
♪ Yet still cannot undo one beat
of my heart's art ♪

35:38.200 --> 35:41.910
♪ I've traveled so far—
the day I find you again ♪

35:41.930 --> 35:45.630
♪ I fear you might have forgotten me ♪

35:44.230 --> 35:45.230
If you trust me,

35:45.880 --> 35:48.700
♪ I fear no doom of endless karmic pain ♪

35:46.200 --> 35:47.260
let me be your eyes.

35:48.730 --> 35:51.220
♪ Only that you drift far from my side ♪

35:51.490 --> 35:55.650
♪ Apart from you,
the world is an endless night ♪

35:55.670 --> 35:59.270
♪ Even if my beating heart
wears thin and fades ♪

35:59.520 --> 36:01.290
♪ I'd choose this fate
till death's final line ♪

36:00.110 --> 36:00.770
You forgot.

36:01.280 --> 36:02.150
You are also my friend.

36:01.520 --> 36:04.140
♪ I only hope the mortal lands ♪

36:04.170 --> 36:06.830
♪ Can grant our wishes ♪

36:04.360 --> 36:05.760
It's quite hard to let go.

36:07.090 --> 36:11.330
♪ Through endless night,
let heaven and earth fall apart ♪

36:11.660 --> 36:15.830
♪ I'd bid farewell to every worldly part ♪

36:16.140 --> 36:20.980
♪ Just to gaze upon you one last time ♪

36:31.840 --> 36:33.510
Have you done what I told you?

36:34.000 --> 36:35.110
As you instructed, My Lady,

36:35.110 --> 36:37.030
the item has been delivered
to the Eagle King.

36:37.030 --> 36:37.510
Good.

36:38.150 --> 36:39.360
If anyone asks later,

36:39.380 --> 36:41.070
just say I went
to the South Street Bookstore

36:41.070 --> 36:42.280
to buy books for Yuanji.

36:42.280 --> 36:43.400
You don't know anything else.

36:43.400 --> 36:46.130
-Especially don't let Xiao Wuyi know.
-Morning.

36:50.510 --> 36:51.210
What are you doing?

36:51.210 --> 36:52.340
Where are you going?

36:52.510 --> 36:53.480
First to the South Street Bookstore

36:53.480 --> 36:54.630
to buy books for Yuanji,

36:54.630 --> 36:55.480
then to Renhe Hall

36:55.480 --> 36:57.190
to fetch the newly arrived cassia seeds
for Ruisheng.

36:57.190 --> 36:58.230
After that, to Xinghua Restaurant

36:58.230 --> 36:59.690
to buy mint cakes for Ziqi.

37:01.770 --> 37:03.510
What about you? Where are you going?

37:03.510 --> 37:04.240
To the palace

37:05.000 --> 37:08.070
to continue discussing
the peace talks with Northern Qin.

37:08.070 --> 37:09.150
After you.

37:09.510 --> 37:10.710
Your business is more important.

37:10.710 --> 37:11.770
I won't bother you.

37:19.090 --> 37:21.640
[Xiyue Restaurant]

37:22.630 --> 37:24.320
-Great!
-Great!

37:28.510 --> 37:29.670
During the storytelling just now,

37:29.670 --> 37:31.880
you said you had seen
the Phoenix Heart Token.

37:31.880 --> 37:32.710
Of course.

37:33.670 --> 37:34.550
Come with me.

37:36.290 --> 37:38.630
[Honglu Temple]

37:41.920 --> 37:43.590
Xiao Wuyi's little beauty.

37:44.480 --> 37:45.480
What a rare guest.

37:47.030 --> 37:49.630
You sent someone
to deliver refined iron to me.

37:49.760 --> 37:51.290
What's the meaning of this?

37:52.190 --> 37:53.590
Where did this come from?

37:53.630 --> 37:54.360
I smelted it.

37:56.230 --> 37:57.550
First, forged at a high temperature

37:57.550 --> 37:58.800
to remove all impurities,

37:58.800 --> 38:00.530
then quenched in green liquor.

38:01.840 --> 38:02.440
I know

38:03.030 --> 38:05.830
you want
the smelting technique for refined iron.

38:09.590 --> 38:12.250
Are you really going
to give me the refined iron?

38:12.480 --> 38:13.230
Not exactly.

38:13.230 --> 38:14.590
I just used this refined iron as bait

38:14.590 --> 38:15.800
to lure you to meet me.

38:18.510 --> 38:19.570
Are you playing me?

38:19.890 --> 38:20.820
I wouldn't dare.

38:21.510 --> 38:23.710
Princess Pingning is my close friend.

38:25.940 --> 38:27.260
So it's about this.

38:28.590 --> 38:30.920
I didn't expect Princess Pingning's life

38:31.440 --> 38:32.640
to be quite valuable.

38:33.400 --> 38:34.840
You want to marry Pingning

38:34.840 --> 38:36.230
just to vent your anger

38:36.480 --> 38:37.610
and regain dignity.

38:38.670 --> 38:42.330
If you are interested in
the smelting technique for refined iron,

38:43.550 --> 38:45.210
then I'll make a deal with you.

38:45.400 --> 38:45.770
No,

38:47.000 --> 38:47.660
a business.

38:51.000 --> 38:52.000
I'm all ears.

39:08.360 --> 39:09.160
Your Majesty.

39:09.650 --> 39:12.850
[Shao Yang, the Empress Dowager
of the Northern Qin]

39:10.110 --> 39:11.710
I've heard so much about you.

39:16.320 --> 39:18.450
I thought I caught someone's slip-up,

39:20.840 --> 39:21.900
but I didn't expect

39:22.440 --> 39:24.280
that it was I who made a mistake.

39:25.000 --> 39:26.800
Your Highness, if you hadn't

39:27.000 --> 39:29.530
eliminated Northern Qin's spy strongholds,

39:30.960 --> 39:32.150
these two fools

39:33.920 --> 39:36.840
wouldn't have been discovered so easily.

39:38.320 --> 39:39.780
Being a spy

39:41.230 --> 39:43.030
still needs experience.

39:43.480 --> 39:45.480
Why did you come here, Your Majesty?

39:46.150 --> 39:48.280
Is it also for the Phoenix Heart Token?

39:49.670 --> 39:50.670
If I say

39:51.670 --> 39:53.070
I got tired of the Capital

39:53.800 --> 39:56.070
and came to Southern Ye
to enjoy the scenery,

39:56.070 --> 39:57.200
will you believe me?

39:58.230 --> 39:59.030
I won't.

40:01.890 --> 40:03.820
Then that's the only excuse I have.

40:05.510 --> 40:06.360
Speak.

40:07.000 --> 40:09.260
Your Highness, why did you want to see me?

40:09.800 --> 40:11.280
Are you trying to tell me

40:11.280 --> 40:13.070
where the Phoenix Heart Token is?

40:13.070 --> 40:14.870
I hope you can stop the Eagle King

40:14.920 --> 40:16.850
from marrying Princess Pingning.

40:17.550 --> 40:21.360
A political marriage between Northern Qin
and Ye is a long-term strategy.

40:21.360 --> 40:23.560
You have been in the military for years.

40:23.920 --> 40:25.110
Don't you understand

40:25.110 --> 40:26.710
that peace benefits both?

40:27.110 --> 40:28.760
You must know better than I do

40:29.840 --> 40:31.480
that the emperor of Northern Qin
and the Eagle King

40:31.480 --> 40:33.590
are only sovereign and subject
on the surface.

40:33.590 --> 40:35.110
The Eagle King has heavily armed himself,

40:35.110 --> 40:36.670
and you support the emperor.

40:36.670 --> 40:39.130
That's why the Northern Qin court
is stable.

40:40.440 --> 40:42.000
But if you pass away

40:42.320 --> 40:44.510
and the Eagle King forms
a marriage alliance with Ye,

40:44.510 --> 40:45.840
marrying the sister of the current Regent,

40:45.840 --> 40:47.230
Prince Qi,

40:47.840 --> 40:49.440
once he has Jiankang's help,

40:49.670 --> 40:51.200
the balance will be broken.

40:52.030 --> 40:52.760
In that case,

40:53.480 --> 40:54.680
how can you guarantee

40:55.030 --> 40:56.360
the Eagle King's troops

40:56.590 --> 40:58.590
will still be Northern Qin's sword?

41:04.000 --> 41:05.630
You make a valid point.

41:08.000 --> 41:11.330
But even if my son and I
have disagreements with the Eagle King,

41:11.330 --> 41:13.530
it's not for an outsider to manipulate.

41:14.630 --> 41:16.830
Such an obvious attempt to sow discord—

41:17.550 --> 41:19.510
are you being too impatient?

41:21.360 --> 41:22.420
Just a suggestion.

41:33.280 --> 41:34.080
Your Majesty.

41:40.440 --> 41:42.900
Thank you for your kindness,
Your Highness.

41:43.000 --> 41:45.440
Then I will also tell you something.

41:46.480 --> 41:48.480
Your Secondary Consort, Xie Jiayu,

41:48.590 --> 41:50.190
for the political marriage,

41:50.920 --> 41:54.150
is secretly meeting the Eagle King
at Honglu Temple right now.

41:54.150 --> 41:55.000
I heard

41:55.880 --> 41:58.480
she also prepared a big gift
for the Eagle King.

42:02.360 --> 42:03.760
Please wait, Your Highness.

42:03.760 --> 42:05.220
I have shown my sincerity.

42:05.290 --> 42:07.670
I hope you can carefully
consider the political marriage

42:07.670 --> 42:09.200
and make a good deal with me.

42:09.670 --> 42:11.440
I'll await your good news.

42:12.840 --> 42:13.900
I won't see you out.

42:19.530 --> 42:21.130
No need to see me out. Go back.

42:24.200 --> 42:24.990
Excuse me.

42:27.630 --> 42:28.430
Still acting?

42:30.320 --> 42:33.230
Since when has the South Street Bookstore
been open in Honglu Temple?

42:33.230 --> 42:35.480
Well, I was just...
